textAnnotations.description:
Now,
as Alastair reduced the thrust, the
pitch changed as the nose of the aircraft
dipped slightly. The needle of the speed
recorder orrung gently through 8.0, 7.0, 6.0
before coming to rest at 5.0, "We're a bit
chead of time", " said Marfair, » Ne'll vun
in on minimum engine power"." Geoffrey
smiled. Martein talked of running in when
they were still more than four hundred
miles from their destination.
